.TH MARCEL-SHELL 1 "December 2023" "1.0" "MARCEL-Shell Manual"

.SH NAME
MARCEL-Shell - A simple shell program

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B MARCEL-Shell

.SH DESCRIPTION
MARCEL-Shell is a simple shell program that allows users to execute commands, manage environment variables, and perform basic shell operations.

.SH OPTIONS
 MARCEL-Shell does not currently support any command-line options.

.SH COMMANDS
MARCEL-Shell supports the following built-in commands:

.B exit
Exit the shell.

.B env
Display the environment variables.

.SH USAGE
To run MARCEL-Shell, simply execute the program without any command-line options
.B
$ ./hsh
   
Once in the shell, you can enter commands as you would in a typical shell environment.

.SH EXAMPLES
Run a command:
.B
MARCEL $ ls

Display environment variables:
.B
MARCEL $ env

Exit the shell:
.B
MARCEL $ exit

